  ('harlot', 'Harlot', 'Гетера', 'Each night*, choose a living player: if they agree, you learn their character, but you both might die.', 'Each night*, choose a living player: if they agree, you learn their character, but you both might die.', 'traveller', 'snv', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chizmw/json-on-the-clocktower/main/data/images/harlot.png', '{"firstNight":null,"firstNightReminder":null,"otherNight":null,"otherNightReminder":"The Harlot points at any player. Then, put the Harlot to sleep. Wake the chosen player, show them the ''This character selected you'' token, then the Harlot token. That player either nods their head yes or shakes their head no. If they nodded their head yes, wake the Harlot and show them the chosen player''s character token. Then, you may decide that both players die.","setup":false,"reminders":["Dead"]}'),
  ('harpy', 'Harpy', 'Гарпія', 'Each night, choose 2 players: tomorrow, the 1st player is mad that the 2nd is evil, or both might die.', 'Each night, choose 2 players: tomorrow, the 1st player is mad that the 2nd is evil, or both might die.', 'minion', 'experimental', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chizmw/json-on-the-clocktower/main/data/images/harpy.png', '{"firstNight":30,"firstNightReminder":"Wake the Harpy; they point at one player, then another. Wake the 1st player the Harpy pointed to, show them the ''This character has selected you'' card, show them the Harpy token, then point at the 2nd player the Harpy pointed to.","otherNight":18,"otherNightReminder":"Wake the Harpy; they point at one player, then another. Wake the 1st player the Harpy pointed to, show them the ''This character has selected you'' card, show them the Harpy token, then point at the 2nd player the Harpy pointed to.","setup":false,"reminders":["Mad","2nd"]}'),
  ('hatter', 'Hatter', 'Капелюшник', 'If you died today or tonight, the Minion & Demon players may choose new Minion & Demon characters to be.', 'If you died today or tonight, the Minion & Demon players may choose new Minion & Demon characters to be.', 'outsider', 'experimental', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chizmw/json-on-the-clocktower/main/data/images/hatter.png', '{"firstNight":null,"firstNightReminder":null,"otherNight":45,"otherNightReminder":"If the Hatter died today: Wake the Minions and Demon. Show them the ''This Character Selected You'' info token, then the Hatter token. Each player either shakes their head no or points to another character of the same type as their current character.  If a second player would end up with the same character as another player, shake your head no and gesture for them to choose again. Put them to sleep. Change each player to the character they chose.","setup":false,"reminders":["Tea Party Tonight"]}'),
