  ('huntsman', 'Huntsman', 'Мисливець', 'Once per game, at night, choose a living player: the Damsel, if chosen, becomes a not-in-play Townsfolk. [+the Damsel]', 'Once per game, at night, choose a living player: the Damsel, if chosen, becomes a not-in-play Townsfolk. [+the Damsel]', 'townsfolk', 'ks', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/chizmw/json-on-the-clocktower/main/data/images/huntsman.png', '{"firstNight":34,"firstNightReminder":"The Huntsman shakes their head ''no'' or points to a player. If they point to the Damsel, wake that player, show the ''You are'' card and a not-in-play character token.","otherNight":52,"otherNightReminder":"The Huntsman shakes their head ''no'' or points to a player. If they point to the Damsel, wake that player, show the ''You are'' card and a not-in-play character token.","setup":true,"reminders":["No ability"]}'),
